{"tid":1546550,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港催淚彈產地直擊 工人手製彈藥極危險","createTime":"2019-09-06T10:14:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T11:02:13.000Z","uid":303830,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"be31697b9fcbf0e732f24f5c9d067b6e12f95d56","tid":1546550,"uid":303830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T10:14:19.000Z","msg":"<strong>香港催淚彈產地直擊 原來係家族生意 工人手製彈藥極危險</strong><br />\n<br />\n香港近月多宗示威，警方之前公布數字，表示已經發射1800枚催淚彈。<br />\n<br />\n有示威者將催淚彈殼影低放上網，引來地球另一端、網媒BuzzFeed記者嘅興趣︰<br />\n<br />\n上面印住一間叫Nonlethal Technologies嘅公司名，位於賓夕法尼亞洲。<br />\n<br />\n到底係個點嘅地方？催淚彈係點整？<br />\n<br />\n記者就決定去到廠房了解一下。<br />\n<br />\n由於負責人拒絕受訪，記者從前員工、媒體報導以及法庭文件，一窺催淚彈是怎樣煉成的。<br />\n<br />\nNonlethal Technologies原來係家族生意，至少經營三代，而家由一對父子營運。公司加埋唔夠30人，但係一年營業額有8百萬美金。<br />\n<br />\n工作多年嘅前員工話，工廠設備簡陋，機器老化，至少發生過3次大火，燒完之後老闆唔肯起過個新廠房。<br />\n<br />\n仲有好多無報警嘅小火，負責人之一就因為意外，雙手被嚴重燒傷。<br />\n<br />\n而且<span style=\"color: red;\">防護設備欠奉，工人皮膚及呼吸道經常受刺激，尤其是喺夏天，飄散嘅化學品撈埋啲汗，會「乸」到皮膚見紅。</span><br />\n<br />\n有打過工嘅人話，無論做咗幾耐，都覺得難以忍受。勞工部曾經派人調查仲罰埋錢，不過情況冇改善。<br />\n<br />\n另外生產過程都好唔安全，工人話平時要徒手接觸具爆炸性化學品，有專家聽完就話呢類工序應該要自動化，由機械人處理先合符標準。<br />\n<br />\n工人每日返成10個半鐘，早上6點半開工下晝5點收工，但係人工只有$9.5美金（港幣約75元），唔算高薪。<br />\n<br />\n工序刻板又多毛病都有好多人繼續做，都係貪公司一個禮拜出一次糧，而且附近嘅城鎮失業率相當高。<br />\n<br />\n除咗生產供應俾香港警方嘅催淚彈，Nonlethal Technologies亦有出貨畀埃及、巴林同土耳其。<br />\n<br />\n幾年前「阿拉伯之春」民主運動爆發，就試過接到order，生產20萬發催淚彈。<br />\n<br />\n點使用催淚彈固然要關注，但係點解美國又可以容許呢間咁罔顧安全嘅工廠存在？<br />\n<br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/home/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%82%AC%E6%B7%9A%E5%BD%88%E7%94%A2%E5%9C%B0%E7%9B%B4%E6%93%8A-%E5%8E%9F%E4%BE%86%E4%BF%82%E5%AE%B6%E6%97%8F%E7%94%9F%E6%84%8F-%E5%B7%A5%E4%BA%BA%E6%89%8B%E8%A3%BD%E5%BD%88%E8%97%A5%E6%A5%B5%E5%8D%B1%E9%9A%AA-063511094.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fhome%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%2582%25AC%25E6%25B7%259A%25E5%25BD%2588%25E7%2594%25A2%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%259B%25B4%25E6%2593%258A-%25E5%258E%259F%25E4%25BE%2586%25E4%25BF%2582%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E6%2597%258F%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%2584%258F-%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%2589%258B%25E8%25A3%25BD%25E5%25BD%2588%25E8%2597%25A5%25E6%25A5%25B5%25E5%258D%25B1%25E9%259A%25AA-063511094.html&d=%2B76N%2F2LucaPHjeWFFloOr%2Bbr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=f1c37658\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/home/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%82%AC%E6%B7%9A%E5%BD%88%E7%94%A2%E5%9C%B0%E7%9B%B4%E6%93%8A-%E5%8E%9F%E4%BE%86%E4%BF%82%E5%AE%B6%E6%97%8F%E7%94%9F%E6%84%8F-%E5%B7%A5%E4%BA%BA%E6%89%8B%E8%A3%BD%E5%BD%88%E8%97%A5%E6%A5%B5%E5%8D%B1%E9%9A%AA-063511094.html</a><br />\n[/url][/url]"},{"pid":"d0d537c3ecaf1e6046c9777a34e65a0ec338f42f","tid":1546550,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T10:15:45.000Z","msg":"7/9機場更新 求求大家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1545323\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1545323</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fg5HKFh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFg5HKFh.jpg&h=b79850f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=%2B76N%2F2LucaPHjeWFFloOr%2Bbr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=0dec4886\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"6deaec4949e2108fc9d7fb25a142a019ea99d0c7","tid":1546550,"uid":41199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T10:23:15.000Z","msg":"血汗工廠"},{"pid":"cecc8678a90d8c3e2ce94a11b2627da1a943a2aa","tid":1546550,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T10:23:18.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1545337/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1545337/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img sr